  "blurb": "A four-bedroom lagoon-front pool villa in a gated, greenery-wrapped resort enclave at Laguna, Bang Tao — a private infinity pool, a Jacuzzi terrace and two entertainment decks, with Thai-inspired interiors and floor-to-ceiling windows framing the water. White-sand beaches, golf and world-class dining a short stroll away.",
  "detail": "Set in the heart of the Laguna resort lands at Bang Tao — one of Asia’s finest integrated destinations — this four-bedroom villa sits within a secure, gated community wrapped in lush tropical greenery, a tranquil oasis a short walk from pristine white-sand beaches and a serene lagoon laced with walking and cycling paths.\n\nThe single-level home is laid out around a spacious open-plan living and dining area bathed in natural light, with four en-suite bedrooms dressed in premium linens and a fully-equipped kitchen for everything from casual breakfasts to gourmet evenings.\n\nOutdoors is built for gathering: a private infinity pool, a shaded terrace with a Jacuzzi, two entertainment decks and a garden, all framed by floor-to-ceiling glass. The interiors carry an elegant Thai sensibility — polished timber, iridescent stone detailing and views of the lagoon from nearly every room.\n\nSmart-home technology, high-speed WiFi and Smart TVs come as standard, with a 24-hour concierge on call and access to the resort spa, the nearby golf course and Laguna’s restaurants and boutiques. Optional private chef, babysitting and in-villa spa can be arranged. The villa is family-friendly, with child-safety measures and cribs or high chairs on request; it is non-smoking, and pets are not permitted.\n\nPlease note: construction is currently under way nearby within the residences, Monday to Saturday between 8am and 5pm, so there may be intermittent daytime noise in the surrounding area during those hours.",
